elements.2211.03119_b782a45c6d52f3480ea1c92eb8bdb: The Second Competition on Spatial Statistics for Large Datasets]
elements.2211.03119_c709441036f9fbe9be8679a8f7e61: In the last few decades, the size of spatial and spatio-temporal datasets in many research areas has rapidly increased with the development of data collection technologies
elements.2211.03119_f9792d67aacc4dabddf6ebc075606: As a result, classical statistical methods in spatial statistics are facing computational challenges
elements.2211.03119_6f8c041a38cbc6c95594b4ef9cde4: For example, the kriging predictor in geostatistics becomes prohibitive on traditional hardware architectures for large datasets as it requires high computing power and memory footprint when dealing with large dense matrix operations
elements.2211.03119_954631a89d449ed63249d1b06342f: Over the years, various approximation methods have been proposed to address such computational issues, however, the community lacks a holistic process to assess their approximation efficiency
elements.2211.03119_299f763e39a5be5358bc2e4ecd817: To provide a fair assessment, in 2021, we organized the first competition on spatial statistics for large datasets, generated by our
elements.2211.03119_d562f3b3bd58d263a66a04a8a61ba: software, and asked participants to report the results of estimation and prediction
elements.2211.03119_1266dc2ae6871f24bf4db903d40b3: Thanks to its widely acknowledged success and at the request of many participants, we organized the second competition in 2022 focusing on predictions for more complex spatial and spatio-temporal processes, including univariate nonstationary spatial processes, univariate stationary space-time processes, and bivariate stationary spatial processes
elements.2211.03119_e6dd0a5211ae92e4ea571ab4c8270: In this paper, we describe in detail the data generation procedure and make the valuable datasets publicly available for a wider adoption
elements.2211.03119_da10b4cbacfe0b985ea7da116fe2f: Then, we review the submitted methods from fourteen teams worldwide, analyze the competition outcomes, and assess the performance of each team.

elements.2211.03119_05d84120161830e3924811e16b6b7: This work proposed a framework for designing and assessing a competition for predicting missing values in large spatial and spatio-temporal datasets
elements.2211.03119_7abf27af1cba39998e3ac8129bf97: software, very large datasets with various settings were generated from popular spatial and spatio-temporal models with exact computations
elements.2211.03119_277b9b9e6ab5b30355f290b874afe: We have made all the datasets publicly available online (
elements.2211.03119_6a0d9b9c48575b1008ce9bbbfe265: ) for future assessments of other existing or new methods as needed
elements.2211.03119_8e695dc8f5f5f46406ff64f3e8ef2: This work also serves as a reference for comparing new results with the results obtained in this study
elements.2211.03119_b61aaa37486cbc85c3ebeb06fc614: The competition covered three types of data: nonstationary spatial data, stationary space-time data, and bivariate stationary spatial data
elements.2211.03119_3d2a88c2212dae1bf1a6e03862f70: We have reviewed the methods used by each participating team and ranked their performances based on prediction accuracy
elements.2211.03119_44cf6d35f78f137ffb88cf02eed53: The ranks provide a fair comparison among these teams, which may shed light on developing even better prediction methods
elements.2211.03119_e19776a01e19742b6ea82fe405567: In the process of evaluating the performance of different teams, we noticed the two top performers
elements.2211.03119_32c63683ef14a9f596b71e58d9a13: in Sub-competitions 2a and 2b, outperforming other teams by a large margin
elements.2211.03119_86f9b19ad8437c39e61698b8eb756: After contacting them, we learned that both teams had combined several datasets from the same sub-competition to perform predictions
elements.2211.03119_c37398d064234d6b8e71c603950f6: Since the same model actually generated different datasets in each sub-competition, the prediction accuracy was significantly improved by combing datasets
elements.2211.03119_af38a820b56474fbee6a49b38db0d: Therefore, we decided to exclude both teams from the leaderboard of Sub-competition 2 for fair comparisons
elements.2211.03119_c832a9cf771997d24c529528e4064: We believe this was a unintended flaw in the competition and such data-generating problems should be avoided in future competitions
elements.2211.03119_db57861232ce5e7c39737b8dcd0fb: For the second year, we had another successful competition with a wonderful response from the community
elements.2211.03119_9ddddf735edf122f7d7e3b570927c: We believe that conducting such competitions provides opportunities for researchers to assess their methods on the same large datasets that are generated by exact computations
elements.2211.03119_38d9137d3112683421bd75750755b: These datasets are valuable to the community, and we have made them publicly available
elements.2211.03119_921081237901eac1687a6e7e66c15: We also believe it is worthwhile to build benchmarking tools to assess the performance of existing approximation methods, which will significantly help to better understand the advantages and disadvantages of these methods
elements.2211.03119_04f04fb4cc728223e6edf0a40d34b: Although we focused on point forecasts, there is value in probabilistic forecasting for uncertainty quantification purpose and we plan to explore this topic in a future competition.
